                     <expan>John</expan>
                  </choice> Ross</name>: <name type="person">Samuel Riley</name> an Interpreter in the <name type="place">Cherokee Agency</name> the articles of merchandize stated in the above Invoice amounting to Six hundred  twenty nine dollars  fifty cents which we gratefully acknowledge to have <choice>
                  <orig>recieved</orig>
                  <reg>received</reg>
               </choice> as a testimony of the continued care of our Father the President of the <name type="place">United States</name> for the <name type="person">Cherokees</name> removed to this Country. <add place="supralinear"> that he holds us fast by the hand.</add> dated at the<pb n="2" facs="pa0030b.small.jpg"/>
               <name type="place">Arkansa River</name> the <date when="1813-03-13">13th day of March 1813.</date>
            </p>
